Tasks

    Today we will make an audio recorder, it's just like the video recorder that we made on the course, but only with [audio:true], [video:false].  '

    The user will also be able to download the recording file when the recording is over.

    Features:

        Record for maximum 5 seconds.
        Show the user a preview of the recording to listen to it on the website (make an audio player)
        Make buttons to [Start Recording] and [Download Recording] when the recording is over.
